制品，尤其要控制低脂牛奶以及油炸食品的摄入。 视频来源：央视网快看 【够科普】护肤品用得越多越勤皮肤或越差"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-89438e0ddb10f6f74e7e2d6ee6a018e5_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/499260165"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I5KfF7aqinLlJEAMaCDczMjI3OTY4IM3GzIwGMAA4S0Apcgk0OTkyNjAxNjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1637186832.7195747", "card_id": "Q_493893285", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么适合冬季用的男生洗面奶？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今年双 11 想剁手，大家帮我推荐下"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-f4dca458b8bbc26cd780a1b009392889_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493893285"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I5KfF7aqinLlJEAMaCDcyMDM1Mzc5ILHAyYsGMAE4OEAqcgk0OTM4OTMyODV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1637186832.7200606", "card_id": "Q_485883005", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 194}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一个人为什么会突然就变的冷漠了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-db77f8495ea5ac1f633902d007537007_720w.jpg?source=2044ae36"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485883005"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5KfF7aqinLlJEAMaCDcwMjU1NjIxINnR6okGMAQ40gRAK3IJNDg1ODgzMDA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1637186832.7204792", "card_id": "Q_499046025", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "旅行中的哪一刻你意识到了「这世界比想象中宽阔」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, 